title: [Frozen Bramble Patch]
description: A vast rolling sea of thick, heavy brambles lies before you, over six feet high, and an indeterminate distance deep.  The brambles are as black as pitch and covered with a thin sheen of ice that lends an evil gleam to the already vicious-looking thorns.
